安装github软件
##########配置用户信息
#提交时的用户和用户名
git config --global user.name "test"
git config --global user.email "user@test.com"
##########创建一个repository(仓库)
mkdir www
cd www
#sets up the necessary git files
#Initialized empty Git repository in www
git init
##########添加文件，提交
git add test.php
git commit test.php "just for test"

##########Push your commit################
#So far everything you've done has been in your local #repository, meaning you still haven't done anything on #GitHub yet. To connect your local repository to your #GitHub account, you will need to set a remote for your #repository and push your commits to it:
#######################################
#给远程repository起一个别名origin
git remote add origin https://github.com/username/Hello-World.git
#sends your commits in the "master" branch to Github
git push origin master

#######################################
使用在其它地方使用
ssh-keygen -t rsa -C "注释"
将.ssh/id_rsa.pub拷贝到github网站

拷贝代码git clone git@github.com:snakerkill/hello.git


